attributes.background:
This petition asks merely for an open discussion between a Government and its people about a different way of living in the future.
Potential problems with the proposed model would be discussed, whilst reflecting upon our current system and attempting to find some common ground.


The Venus Project is an organisation promoting an alternative global model based around the notion of a Resource-Based Economy. 
This means analysing the Earth's natural resources, collating the research into an inventory and thinking logically about how the resources should be used.

The main goals are:
to create easily sustainable, environmentally-friendly food and energy supplies;
to use technology to replace unnecessary Human effort;
to create a social environment where crime is unnecessary;
to create products that are built to last (not replaced by a newer model immediately) eradicating mountains of resource waste;
and allow the Human race to be free to spend more time as a global community.
